Could I have some bacon?

806
01:11:20,371 --> 01:11:22,471
Want a tomato, Sam?

807
01:11:22,871 --> 01:11:26,471
- What are you doing?!
- Tomatoes, sausages, nice crispy bacon.

808
01:11:26,771 --> 01:11:29,371
- We saved some for you, Mr. Frodo.
- Put it out, you fools!

809
01:11:29,671 --> 01:11:33,471
- Put it out!
- That's nice! Ash on my tomatoes!

810
01:11:42,071 --> 01:11:43,772
Go!

