[Sindarin] <i>Andelu i ven.</i>
[English] The road is too dangerous.

859
01:20:02,091 --> 01:20:03,291
What are they saying?

860
01:20:03,081 --> 01:20:05,621
[Sindarin] <i>Frodo fîr. Ae athradon i hîr ...</i>
[English] Frodo is dying. If I cross the river ...

861
01:20:05,621 --> 01:20:08,841
[Sindarin] <i>... tûr gwaith nîn beriatha hon.</i>
[English] ... the power of my people will protect him.

862
01:20:09,491 --> 01:20:10,991
I do not fear them.

863
01:20:14,711 --> 01:20:16,163
[Sindarin] <i>Be iest lîn.</i>
[English] As you wish.

864
01:20:20,992 --> 01:20:22,392
Arwen...

865
01:20:22,392 --> 01:20:25,592
...ride hard. Don't Look back.

866
